description: This top 2% rating Cooter purrs with a rating of 87, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 87, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Leverage for East, Box for South, and 8 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [87 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
